-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3819535">Hyde Park的头条新闻</a>。任何剩余的门票都可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/sabrina-carpenter-tickets/artist/2001092" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。</p><p>在其他新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dolly-parton">多莉·帕顿（Dolly Parton）</a>透露，她在同意出现在其协作版本的“请请请请”之前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dolly-parton-laid-down-some-rules-to-sabrina-carpenter-over-please-please-please-collaboration-i-dont-say-dirty-words-on-camera-3848001">，向Sabrina Carpenter制定了一些基本规则</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sabrina-carpenter-and-dolly-partons-new-please-please-please-collab-3837970">这位歌手与乡村偶像合作，共同创作了</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carpenter-announces-deluxe-version-of-short-n-sweet-featuring-dolly-parton-3834745">Carpenter最新专辑“ Short N&#39;Sweet”的豪华版</a>，上个月发行的豪华版。</p><p>在接受<em><a href="https://www.knoxnews.com/story/entertainment/music/2025/03/18/dolly-parton-talks-about-working-with-beyonce-sabrina-carpenter/82490811007/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">诺克斯新闻</a>采访时，</em>帕顿说她告诉了卡彭特，然后同意了协作：“我告诉她，我说，&#39;现在，我不说，我不会取笑耶稣。我对上帝的说话不好，而且我在相机上不说肮脏的话，但是我知道如果我发疯了，我就知道了<em>。</em> ”</p><p>邮政<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chancellor-rachel-reeves-defends-accepting-free-sabrina-carpenter-tickets-3849304">总理雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）捍卫接受免费Sabrina Carpenter门票的</a>辩护首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
